#As a customer, I want to be able to add a product to the shopping cart, so that I can buy it.

Feature: Add more than one product to the shopping cart
  As a customer I should be able to add more than one product to the shopping cart
  so that I can by the product.

  Background: Going to Willys and pressing the accept cookies button
    Given that I am on "https://www.willys.se"
    And I click the accept cookies button
    And we have been through the initial select delivery popup
    Then I should be able to see some products

  Scenario: Add a product by clicking plus more then one time
    When I click the plus sign more then once for a product
    And click the shopping cart
    Then I should see a quantity of more then one of the products in the shopping cart

  Scenario: Add a product by changing quantity to to two manually
    When I change the quantity of a product from zero to two
    Then I should see a quantity of one of the product in the shopping cart